1891
02:28:25,963 --> 02:28:29,093
Raja, look at your pathetic condition.

1892
02:28:29,330 --> 02:28:31,773
Why are you ruining yourself
for that disloyal woman?

1893
02:28:32,445 --> 02:28:33,607
Leave me alone, Daddy.

1894
02:28:33,648 --> 02:28:35,961
How do I leave you alone?
I am your father after all.

1895
02:28:36,440 --> 02:28:37,286
Come with me.

1896
02:28:37,684 --> 02:28:39,843
We will teach such a lesson
to that girl and her father...

1897
02:28:39,884 --> 02:28:41,411
...that they will remember
it throughout their lives.

1898
02:28:41,654 --> 02:28:43,218
I will get you married very pompously.

1899
02:28:43,348 --> 02:28:45,577
Your wedding procession will pass
from the front of that girl's house.

1900
02:28:45,618 --> 02:28:46,625
You'll see.

1901
02:28:47,592 --> 02:28:50,689
Whether it is my funeral
or wedding procession...

1902
02:28:51,723 --> 02:28:53,146
...doesn't make any difference to me.

1903
02:28:54,181 --> 02:28:55,827
You are free to do whatever you want.

1904
02:29:01,776 --> 02:29:03,926
Look, read it yourself.

1905
02:29:04,626 --> 02:29:07,976
The person for whom you cry day and night,
your Raja...

1906
02:29:08,235 --> 02:29:09,635
...is going to get married once again.

1907
02:29:12,861 --> 02:29:14,034
[SOBBING]

1908
02:29:15,352 --> 02:29:16,814
Shakti! What happened?

1909
02:29:20,035 --> 02:29:21,596
He has shown his true colours.

1910
02:29:22,338 --> 02:29:25,268
[SOBBING]

1911
02:29:27,892 --> 02:29:28,885
Madhu...

1912
02:29:31,709 --> 02:29:34,016
...for how long will you live this way?

1913
02:29:35,526 --> 02:29:37,600
I am unable to bear
this condition of yours.

1914
02:29:38,923 --> 02:29:41,150
Child, your entire life is ahead of you.

1915
02:29:41,843 --> 02:29:43,341
Forget whatever has happened.

1916
02:29:45,068 --> 02:29:46,696
Start life afresh.

1917
02:29:48,541 --> 02:29:49,700
Get married to Shakti.

1918
02:29:50,444 --> 02:29:51,558
No, Daddy.

1919
02:29:52,235 --> 02:29:54,501
Never ever say it again.

1920
02:29:55,431 --> 02:29:56,907
Leave me to my condition.

1921
02:29:57,905 --> 02:29:58,744
Dear!

1922
02:30:00,683 --> 02:30:02,507
How can I leave you in this state?

1923
02:30:03,177 --> 02:30:04,275
I'm your father.

1924
02:30:04,652 --> 02:30:06,457
I want your happiness.

1925
02:30:08,141 --> 02:30:09,820
You want to see me happy, right?

1926
02:30:09,899 --> 02:30:10,558
Yes.

1927
02:30:11,864 --> 02:30:14,523
Then please take me away from this place.

1928
02:30:17,088 --> 02:30:18,575
[SOBBING]

1929
02:30:18,616 --> 02:30:24,107
Yes, dear. I'll take you.

1930
02:30:25,376 --> 02:30:26,528
I'll take you far away.

1931
02:30:26,907 --> 02:30:28,040
The auspicious time of the
engagement is passing by.

1932
02:30:28,081 --> 02:30:29,491
Your son hasn't come until now.

1933
02:30:29,715 --> 02:30:30,987
Raja might be on his way.

1934
02:30:31,276 --> 02:30:33,976
But you have done all the arrangements,
isn't it?

1935
02:30:34,415 --> 02:30:36,825
You need not worry at all, Hazari Prasad.

1936
02:30:37,086 --> 02:30:38,582
I have done all the arrangements.

1937
02:30:38,756 --> 02:30:40,451
I remember my promise very well.

1938
02:30:40,652 --> 02:30:41,292
Radhe Shyam!

1939
02:30:53,633 --> 02:30:54,798
Thank you. Thank you.

1940
02:30:55,016 --> 02:30:56,630
This is nothing at all, Hazari Prasad.

1941
02:30:56,765 --> 02:30:59,280
These are the gifts for the groom.
It is not the actual dowry.

1942
02:30:59,579 --> 02:31:01,137
Let the marriage take place once.

1943
02:31:01,232 --> 02:31:02,803
You will see that you
will not find place in...

1944
02:31:02,844 --> 02:31:03,709
...your house to keep all these things.

1945
02:31:03,750 --> 02:31:05,420
For now I'll go and
find a place to keep this.

1946
02:31:05,461 --> 02:31:07,074
Excuse me. Thank you. Thank you.

1947
02:31:07,190 --> 02:31:11,030
I will keep so much money with me.
Oh my Goddess!

1948
02:31:11,148 --> 02:31:14,895
- Oh my Goddess!
- Listen, what are you doing for money?

1949
02:31:15,134 --> 02:31:17,570
You are getting my Raja
married to a mad girl.

1950
02:31:17,611 --> 02:31:19,667
All the girls are basically mad.
Look at yourself.

1951
02:31:19,867 --> 02:31:21,899
If you were not mad then would
you say such unfortunate things...

1952
02:31:21,940 --> 02:31:23,317
...on the occasion of
your son's engagement?

1953
02:31:23,402 --> 02:31:26,217
Do you know what my son
is going through right now?

1954
02:31:26,569 --> 02:31:29,180
He is heart broken.

1955
02:31:29,705 --> 02:31:31,261
He has started drinking liquor.

1956
02:31:31,302 --> 02:31:34,667
Do you know,
he has not come back home since last night.

1957
02:31:34,837 --> 02:31:36,264
But you are not at all bothered about him.

1958
02:31:36,744 --> 02:31:38,549
Have mercy on your child!

1959
02:31:38,635 --> 02:31:40,699
- Don't be so cruel to him!
- Stop your rubbish!

1960
02:31:41,146 --> 02:31:42,671
I know what I am doing. Okay?

1961
02:31:47,044 --> 02:31:50,232
Last time when I wanted to sell this coat,
Mr. Pasricha.

1962
02:31:50,495 --> 02:31:52,079
I thought that...

1963
02:31:52,120 --> 02:31:53,856
Who is Mr. Hazari Prasad amongst you all?

1964
02:31:55,365 --> 02:31:56,897
It's me. What is the matter?

1965
02:31:57,308 --> 02:31:58,619
Is this the photograph of your son?

1966
02:31:59,517 --> 02:32:01,314
Yes. This is my son Raja's photograph.

1967
02:32:01,962 --> 02:32:03,023
What's the matter, Inspector?

1968
02:32:03,153 --> 02:32:04,950
What has happened to him? Is he all right?

1969
02:32:05,014 --> 02:32:06,330
Your son has met with an accident.

1970
02:32:06,496 --> 02:32:08,966
- We have recovered all these things
from his dead body. - No!

1971
02:32:09,050 --> 02:32:10,717
This is a lie! A lie!

1972
02:32:10,750 --> 02:32:13,791
Then you confirm it yourself.
Constable, bring the body inside.

1973
02:32:35,273 --> 02:32:36,601
No!

1974
02:32:36,642 --> 02:32:38,054
[SOBBING]

1975
02:32:38,835 --> 02:32:39,737
My Raja!

1976
02:32:42,025 --> 02:32:43,315
Raja!

1977
02:32:44,192 --> 02:32:46,381
My son Raja!

1978
02:32:54,017 --> 02:32:56,590
Now be assured! Be assured!

1979
02:32:57,468 --> 02:32:59,542
You killer! You sinner!

1980
02:33:00,182 --> 02:33:02,329
You have killed my son.

1981
02:33:03,164 --> 02:33:05,929
You have separated Raja and Madhu.

1982
