When my son was fighting against
life and death in the hospital...

1984
02:33:15,626 --> 02:33:18,360
...then instead of saving you son's life...

1985
02:33:18,747 --> 02:33:22,818
...you made a deal with
Madhu regarding her husband.

1986
02:33:23,081 --> 02:33:24,985
You took away her husband from her.

1987
02:33:25,026 --> 02:33:30,709
This is her curse which has
separated my son from me today.

1988
02:33:31,483 --> 02:33:36,318
Now sell this corpse also in the market.

1989
02:33:36,646 --> 02:33:39,513
Maybe you will get some
money with that also.

1990
02:33:39,708 --> 02:33:45,339
You have killed him.
Now sell him off. Sell him of.

1991
02:33:46,873 --> 02:33:47,888
My son!

1992
02:33:47,995 --> 02:33:48,938
RAJA: Mother!

1993
02:33:50,715 --> 02:33:56,406
[INTENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

1994
02:33:56,926 --> 02:33:59,911
My son, Raja! Raja!

1995
02:34:00,155 --> 02:34:03,358
You are alive, my son?

1996
02:34:03,901 --> 02:34:05,077
Yes, Mother.

1997
02:34:06,567 --> 02:34:09,076
My Raja is alive.

1998
02:34:10,705 --> 02:34:13,002
My son is alive.

1999
02:34:15,612 --> 02:34:16,773
He is alive.

2000
02:34:17,115 --> 02:34:20,023
Mr. Raja,
how did your clothes come on this corpse?

2001
02:34:22,880 --> 02:34:24,437
I had drunk and I was lying unconscious.

2002
02:34:26,427 --> 02:34:28,886
At that time,
he must have stolen my coat and my chain.

2003
02:34:29,836 --> 02:34:31,565
Then he must have met with an accident.

2004
02:34:34,566 --> 02:34:35,784
I wish that I had died instead of him.

2005
02:34:35,916 --> 02:34:38,328
- No, Son. You should never say that.
- Don't touch me!

2006
02:34:39,215 --> 02:34:39,647
But, son...

2007
02:34:39,687 --> 02:34:41,877
Dare if you will call me a son.
Or even if you will touch me.

2008
02:34:42,074 --> 02:34:45,307
- But son, I have done all this for you.
- Not for me, Mr. Hazari Prasad.

2009
02:34:46,348 --> 02:34:49,728
What am I to you? Just a saleable thing.

2010
02:34:51,277 --> 02:34:53,488
Besides selling me, what else can you do?

2011
02:34:55,541 --> 02:34:57,669
Maybe you had given birth
to me for this reason only.

2012
02:34:59,151 --> 02:35:02,760
As a butcher nurtures and nourishes a goat.

2013
02:35:03,633 --> 02:35:05,591
Then he sells off every piece of his.

2014
02:35:07,235 --> 02:35:09,555
No, Raja. No!
You are under a misunderstanding.

2015
02:35:09,578 --> 02:35:11,308
You are telling lies.

2016
02:35:13,157 --> 02:35:14,601
I have heard everything.

2017
02:35:14,878 --> 02:35:17,477
I heard what you did with Madhu.
What sacrifice you asked her to make?

2018
02:35:19,194 --> 02:35:20,769
Madhu was a stranger.

2019
02:35:22,035 --> 02:35:25,482
But still for the sake of my
life she sacrificed her husband.

2020
02:35:27,636 --> 02:35:31,476
But you. I was your very own blood.

2021
02:35:32,551 --> 02:35:33,933
A part of you.

2022
02:35:35,611 --> 02:35:38,551
Sometimes a hungry lion eats his
own children out of helplessness.

2023
02:35:39,352 --> 02:35:41,927
But what was your helplessness,
Mr. Hazari Prasad?

2024
02:35:42,465 --> 02:35:43,886
What were you hungry for?

2025
02:35:44,027 --> 02:35:44,809
How much hungry were you that...

2026
02:35:44,911 --> 02:35:46,355
...didn't get satisfied even
after eating your own child?

2027
02:35:46,518 --> 02:35:47,934
Stop it, child! Stop it!

2028
02:35:48,444 --> 02:35:50,882
What are you crying for, Mr. Hazari Prasad?

2029
02:35:51,658 --> 02:35:55,125
You had said a few days ago
that you don't have any son.

2030
02:35:55,772 --> 02:35:57,283
That I am not your son.

2031
02:35:57,775 --> 02:36:00,272
Today I admit this in
front of all these people...

2032
02:36:00,968 --> 02:36:03,380
...that after today, you are not my father.

2033
02:36:13,096 --> 02:36:16,322
- Raja!
- Raja, my son, where are you going?

2034
02:36:17,977 --> 02:36:20,435
I am going away from this
suffocation and embarrassment.

2035
02:36:21,024 --> 02:36:21,976
I am going back to my Madhu.

2036
02:36:29,228 --> 02:36:31,274
- Take care of the house.
- Yes, Mother.

2037
02:36:31,299 --> 02:36:32,195
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

2038
02:37:07,241 --> 02:37:08,400
[TYRE SCREECH]

2039
02:37:08,441 --> 02:37:09,189
Hey!

2040
02:37:09,214 --> 02:37:11,307
Where are you going? There's no one inside.

2041
02:37:11,409 --> 02:37:11,847
What?

2042
02:37:12,187 --> 02:37:13,904
- Where did everybody go?
- To the airport.

2043
02:37:13,945 --> 02:37:16,536
Everyone is going to London
forever by the 4 o'clock flight.

2044
02:37:20,061 --> 02:37:23,436
[ENGINE REVVING]

2045
02:38:05,930 --> 02:38:08,324
[ENGINE REVVING]

2046
02:38:12,731 --> 02:38:14,766
Hello. Haji Ali traffic control.

2047
02:38:14,791 --> 02:38:17,028
A boy riding a red bike has jumped
the signal and is running away.

2048
02:38:17,102 --> 02:38:18,546
Get hold of him immediately. Over!

2049
02:38:18,601 --> 02:38:20,242
Received the message. Over and out!

2050
02:38:43,155 --> 02:38:44,293
Are you riding the bike
under the influence of alcohol?

2051
02:38:44,455 --> 02:38:45,587
Sir, I am really in a hurry right now.

2052
02:38:45,679 --> 02:38:46,666
I have to reach the airport immediately.

2053
02:38:46,943 --> 02:38:48,095
Show me the licence.

2054
02:38:49,352 --> 02:38:50,630
Sir, the licence is at home.

2055
02:38:50,806 --> 02:38:51,942
You must have papers for the bike at least.

2056
02:38:52,315 --> 02:38:54,464
Sir, please let me go.
I am in a real hurry.

2057
02:38:54,801 --> 02:38:56,716
- Have you stolen this bike?
- No, sir.

2058
02:38:56,741 --> 02:38:58,181
Sir, I think that there
is something fishy here.

2059
02:38:58,237 --> 02:38:59,454
- No, sir.
- Fine. Arrest him.

2060
02:38:59,555 --> 02:39:00,715
Sir, please try to understand.

2061
02:39:00,775 --> 02:39:02,527
Sir, trust me. Right now it is
the question of my life and death.

2062
02:39:02,552 --> 02:39:04,815
I said, shut up. Come with me. Come.

2063
02:39:06,232 --> 02:39:09,127
What is this nonsense?
Why did you catch his hand?

2064
02:39:09,399 --> 02:39:11,318
Don't you know that I am with him?

2065
02:39:11,729 --> 02:39:14,028
Why are you tormenting
my friend who is also a lover?

2066
02:39:14,066 --> 02:39:16,444
Sir, please help me, sir.
If I don't reach the airport on time...

2067
02:39:16,610 --> 02:39:18,230
...then my Madhu will be
separated from me forever.

2068
02:39:18,393 --> 02:39:19,183
- What are you saying?
- Yes.

2069
02:39:19,269 --> 02:39:20,043
Sir.

2070
02:39:20,115 --> 02:39:21,315
He was breaking all the
traffic rules and running away.

2071
02:39:21,340 --> 02:39:21,804
No, sir.

2072
02:39:21,829 --> 02:39:22,873
I guess, it is a matter of theft.

2073
02:39:23,009 --> 02:39:25,048
Hey! It is not a matter of theft.

2074
02:39:25,075 --> 02:39:26,419
It is a matter of a love affair.

2075
02:39:26,699 --> 02:39:30,356
Hey! When the public is crazy in love...

2076
02:39:30,397 --> 02:39:32,695
...then our law will not
be able to do anything.

2077
02:39:33,195 --> 02:39:35,349
- I got it, sir.
- You got it, right?

2078
02:39:35,430 --> 02:39:37,874
Now no plane will take
off from the airport until.

2079
02:39:37,930 --> 02:39:40,465
I do not drop you at the airport.

2080
02:39:40,837 --> 02:39:42,491
- I will drop you there. Come on.
- Thank you, sir.

2081
02:39:52,475 --> 02:39:54,259
[HORN HONKING]

2082
02:40:05,760 --> 02:40:10,049
[ENGINE REVVING]

2083
02:40:31,875 --> 02:40:36,271
ANNOUNCEMENT: <i>Air India AI 111 is ready
to take off to London.</i>

2084
02:40:36,425 --> 02:40:40,796
<i>The passengers are requested</i>
<i>to proceed to gate number 10.</i>

2085
02:41:22,995 --> 02:41:23,994
- Excuse me, sir.
- Yes.

2086
02:41:24,235 --> 02:41:25,444
The Air India flight,
which was supposed to fly to London.

2087
02:41:25,499 --> 02:41:26,612
Sorry, sir.
The flight has already taken off.

2088
02:41:26,840 --> 02:41:32,325
[AIROPLANE ENGINE WHOOSH]

2089
02:42:00,435 --> 02:42:03,662
Please forgive me, son.

2090
02:42:22,575 --> 02:42:24,958
Take this and put it around her neck.

2091
02:42:53,342 --> 02:42:54,534
Just a minute. Just a minute.

2092
02:42:54,575 --> 02:42:56,831
At least allow Dev Anand
to click a picture.

2093
02:42:57,088 --> 02:42:59,371
- Just a minute. Just a minute.
- Even you can join in, sir.

2094
02:43:01,516 --> 02:43:04,532
"I can't sleep. I have no solace."

2095
02:43:04,586 --> 02:43:06,986
"Somebody, please go and search for me."

2096
02:43:07,038 --> 02:43:10,067
"I don't know where my heart is lost."

2097
02:43:10,108 --> 02:43:13,045
"I don't know where my heart is lost."
